[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm considering whether the provider constructor in a public static class can be public and implicit. Since the default constructor inherits the access level of the class, I think it can indeed be public. I'll also look into JUnit 6 class template support for Native images. Regarding Checkstyle, I should avoid nested non-public tests since they aren’t top-level. Plus, if the `ClassTemplate` is experimental, I want to verify its compile status and ensure proper naming conventions for security.
