[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about when a native test runs, and whether the `java.class.path` is set. It might not be configured properly, which could include the original classpath. In a native image scenario, the `java.class.path` system property might end up being empty or just point to the image classpath. I need to clarify how this impacts the execution of native tests and ensure everything is correctly set up for the environment.
