est class can use JUnit Jupiter class-template APIs required by Spring Test 7’s scanner path.\n\nI did not modify reachability metadata or Native Image config files, and I did not run tests per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05a031c3e22e6398016a284cc0dc948197b5d13ada704f0045\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1107, "output": 837, "cacheRead": 61952, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 63896, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781025965189, "responseId": "resp_05a031c3e22e6398016a284cadd5ec819780881faf7eff2bac"}, "toolResults": []}
